		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">风丘丘游侠快速发射3个风手里剑，前两个较小的均造成<span color="#7fffd7">60%</span><span>伤害，第三枚较大的造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">85%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">风丘丘游侠使用匕首进行居合旋斩，每段分别造成<span color="#7fffd7">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="437" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">风丘丘游侠借助<span textDecoration="underline">风史莱姆</span><span>悬浮空中，在空中用匕首进行3段普通攻击，每段分别造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">80%,80%,100%</span><span>伤害，每段还会斩出伤害相同的风刃。<br/>用非风元素攻击风史莱姆可瘫痪游侠。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1008" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="273" height="20" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">风史莱姆：触碰产生6个对应元素微粒。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/丘丘风行游侠.assets/Image_13.png')" x="720" y="138">
