		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">风丘丘游侠使用匕首进行至多3段的普通攻击，每段分别造成<span color="#7fffd7">60%,60%,80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">风丘丘游侠扔出一枚较大的风手里剑，其会飞回来，接触造成<span color="#7fffd7">85%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#00ae83" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#00ae83">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
